    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "### Highly stiff: $\\mu = 1000$\n\nWith $\\mu = 1000$ the system has sharp transitions where $x$ jumps rapidly between $\\pm 2$. BDF handles this where Adams would struggle.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "mu2 : 1000$\ntspan2 : np_linspace(0.0, 6000.0, 20000)$\n\nres2 : np_cvode([y2, mu2*(1 - x2^2)*y2 - x2],\n                [t, x2, y2], [2.0, 0.0], tspan2,\n                1e-6, 1e-9, bdf)$\n\nt2 : np_slice(res2, all, 0)$\nx2_col : np_slice(res2, all, 1)$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 5,
      "outputs": []
    },
    {
