    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "source": "## 3. ROBER Consistency Check\n\nThe Robertson system conserves total mass: $y_1 + y_2 + y_3 = 1$ for all $t$.",
      "metadata": {}
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": "mass_sum : np_add(s1_col, np_add(s2_col, s3_col))$\nnr : first(np_shape(res3))$\nones : np_ones([nr])$\nprintf(true, \"Max deviation from mass=1: ~,2e~%\",\n       np_max(np_abs(np_sub(mass_sum, ones))))$",
      "metadata": {},
      "execution_count": 10,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "name": "stdout",
          "output_type": "stream",
          "text": [
            "Max deviation from mass=1: 1.66e-13\no171$$\\mathbf{false}$$\nfalse"
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
